1:01:23.291 --> 1:01:24.916
-and independent inquiry...
-Let me help you.

1:01:25.000 --> 1:01:26.708
...into what happened
on the 22nd of July...

1:01:26.791 --> 1:01:28.500
-You OK?
-Yes.

1:01:28.583 --> 1:01:31.000
Our work will begin immediately.
Thank you.

1:01:31.083 --> 1:01:33.416
This inquiry is of vital importance.

1:01:33.875 --> 1:01:36.375
Whatever went wrong, we must confront it.

1:01:36.875 --> 1:01:40.916
If we fail to do so,
the terrorist will surely win.

1:01:41.458 --> 1:01:42.875
Who was that on the phone?

1:01:45.208 --> 1:01:46.500
It was from the office.

1:01:48.416 --> 1:01:50.041
It's the third one tonight.

1:02:25.291 --> 1:02:26.208
Yes?

1:02:31.750 --> 1:02:32.875
I'm Lara.

1:02:33.333 --> 1:02:34.375
-Hi, Lara.
-Hi.

1:02:35.375 --> 1:02:39.125
I was also on the island.
