1:02:42.750 --> 1:02:43.750
How is Viljar?

1:02:47.916 --> 1:02:49.208
He needs to wake up.

1:02:51.000 --> 1:02:51.916
Yeah.

1:02:56.000 --> 1:02:56.958
Are you OK?

1:02:58.625 --> 1:03:00.625
