-Is this true?
-Yes, after September 11th.

1:49:46.416 --> 1:49:48.875
Did you attend this first meeting?

1:49:49.333 --> 1:49:50.166
I did.

1:49:51.875 --> 1:49:52.916
What happened?

1:49:55.291 --> 1:49:56.791
I was given my mission.

1:49:57.250 --> 1:49:58.083
This mission.

1:49:58.166 --> 1:50:02.083
Mr. Breivik, the police have tracked
your movements in 2002

1:50:02.583 --> 1:50:06.333
