1:50:48.125 --> 1:50:51.416
It was built especially for his trial.
So I guess in some way, that's true.

1:50:51.541 --> 1:50:53.708
He can't help but smile at the camera.

1:50:53.791 --> 1:50:55.958
He's in control here while all...

1:50:56.208 --> 1:50:58.333
-No! No, one more.
-One more.

1:50:58.416 --> 1:50:59.416
-One more.
-One more.

1:51:00.125 --> 1:51:04.750
Then I carefully began to assemble
the components of the bomb.

1:51:05.708 --> 1:51:09.291
I did it very slowly, of course,
so that the authorities wouldn't see me.

1:51:09.375 --> 1:51:10.916
Turning to the attacks.

1:51:11.666 --> 1:51:13.125
Did you feel empathy

1:51:13.875 --> 1:51:14.875
for the victims?

1:51:19.500 --> 1:51:21.708
Shall I make this easier for you all?

1:51:23.416 --> 1:51:25.625
I will forgo any appeal,

1:51:26.375 --> 1:51:30.416
any retrial,
I will spare the families all of this,

1:51:31.250 --> 1:51:32.916
if the Court finds me sane.

1:51:46.000 --> 1:51:46.916
Good.

1:51:55.916 --> 1:51:57.625
-Are you OK?
-Yes.

1:51:57.833 --> 1:51:59.583
-I think your parents are here.
-OK.

1:51:59.666 --> 1:52:00.875
See you tomorrow.

1:52:01.541 --> 1:52:02.541
See you tomorrow.

1:52:19.500 --> 1:52:20.583
