1:53:46.166 --> 1:53:47.583
I just want to beat him.

1:53:49.833 --> 1:53:51.541
Then maybe this is your chance.

1:53:58.708 --> 1:54:00.541
Have you ever met the defendant?

1:54:01.208 --> 1:54:03.708
-I met him online.
-Online?

1:54:04.250 --> 1:54:05.666
Yes, online,

1:54:05.750 --> 1:54:09.083
in a chat forum
attached to mythic military games

1:54:09.166 --> 1:54:11.791
like World of Warcraft, Call of Duty.

1:54:12.625 --> 1:54:14.375
It's a place to train.

1:54:14.916 --> 1:54:17.375
-It's a place to share ideas.
-Recruit?

1:54:19.541 --> 1:54:20.375
Of course.

1:54:20.916 --> 1:54:23.458
How did the defendant strike you?

1:54:25.541 --> 1:54:28.333
He liked to lead missions.

1:54:29.583 --> 1:54:30.416
Online.

1:54:32.458 --> 1:54:33.416
Was he rational?

1:54:34.291 --> 1:54:35.125
Perfectly.

1:54:37.041 --> 1:54:38.083
Was he a leader?

1:54:39.208 --> 1:54:40.875
He certainly wanted to be.

1:54:43.583 --> 1:54:46.250
Was Mr. Breivik your leader?

1:54:47.708 --> 1:54:48.750
No, he was not.

1:54:49.333 --> 1:54:51.666
You wouldn't follow Mr. Breivik?

1:54:52.250 --> 1:54:54.875
I think others are better qualified
than him.

1:54:55.500 --> 1:54:57.916
Oh, so, better than Breivik?

1:54:59.000 --> 1:54:59.916
Definitely.

1:55:00.041 --> 1:55:05.125
Would they be capable of doing
what Anders Behring Breivik did?

1:55:06.041 --> 1:55:10.125
The Alt Right, the Far Right,
you can call us whatever you want,

1:55:10.708 --> 1:55:14.041
