1:55:14.125 --> 1:55:16.750
about changing society completely.

1:55:18.500 --> 1:55:21.291
And a single man's violent acts

1:55:22.125 --> 1:55:24.541
won't help us to reach that goal.

1:55:29.041 --> 1:55:30.916
He's a coward. He's a fucking coward.

1:55:33.250 --> 1:55:37.041
I mean, to betray me like that?
You never betray a brother. Never.

1:55:37.958 --> 1:55:40.625
There are millions of people out there
who support me.

1:55:40.833 --> 1:55:42.250
And this is the best you can do?

1:55:42.958 --> 1:55:44.166
He was the only one.

1:55:45.250 --> 1:55:47.958
I'm a Commander
in the Knights Templar Europe.

1:55:56.625 --> 1:55:57.875
What about my mother?

1:56:00.750 --> 1:56:02.458
