1:58:31.666 --> 1:58:33.125
I just lost all that.

1:58:36.333 --> 1:58:37.291
I just...

1:58:38.041 --> 1:58:42.541
had to live in a world of pain and fear...

1:58:44.208 --> 1:58:45.500
and so much anger.

1:58:47.833 --> 1:58:49.708
And I would just-- Sorry.

1:58:52.500 --> 1:58:54.458
I've just been feeling so guilty.

1:58:57.208 --> 1:58:58.833
I just keep on wondering...

1:58:59.791 --> 1:59:02.625
how did I live when she died?

1:59:07.250 --> 1:59:08.166
And...

1:59:09.000 --> 1:59:11.041
And how do I face my parents?

1:59:11.916 --> 1:59:13.791
And what do I say to my brother?

1:59:17.833 --> 1:59:18.833
Then I just...

1:59:20.291 --> 1:59:23.875
I just couldn't understand
why anyone would want to kill us.

1:59:26.958 --> 1:59:29.875
I don't understand
what's so frightening about me.

1:59:34.500 --> 1:59:35.458
Thank you.

1:59:36.916 --> 1:59:38.041
Thank you, Lara.

1:59:59.291 --> 2:00:00.125
You OK?

2:00:01.333 --> 2:00:02.541
Yeah, I'm fine.

