2:01:22.666 --> 2:01:23.583
It's OK.

2:01:25.833 --> 2:01:26.833
So did I.

2:01:34.416 --> 2:01:35.541
How close is he?

2:01:36.875 --> 2:01:38.791
I couldn't see from the TV.

2:01:39.500 --> 2:01:40.625
He's really close.

2:01:42.958 --> 2:01:45.541
You don't have to look at him
if you don't want to.

2:01:49.333 --> 2:01:51.208
Do you know what you're going to say?

2:01:51.333 --> 2:01:54.000
I'm trying to think of things...

2:01:56.208 --> 2:01:57.791
