2:02:00.375 --> 2:02:02.208
I just don't want to be weak.

2:02:02.958 --> 2:02:03.833
That's all.

2:02:04.958 --> 2:02:06.208
Not in front of him.

2:02:15.416 --> 2:02:17.416
You can be weak and still strong.

2:02:18.916 --> 2:02:20.208
You know that, right?

2:02:32.666 --> 2:02:34.083
You're going to be great.

2:02:39.750 --> 2:02:40.666
Thanks.

2:02:45.375 --> 2:02:46.500
I should get back.

2:02:52.041 --> 2:02:54.083
-See you tomorrow?
-See you tomorrow.

2:04:29.791 --> 2:04:31.583
Wait. I just need a minute.

2:04:53.625 --> 2:04:54.541
You OK?

2:04:55.750 --> 2:04:57.125
Yeah, I'm fine.

2:05:01.833 --> 2:05:02.666
Thank you.

