2:10:56.625 --> 2:10:57.666
I survived.

2:11:01.833 --> 2:11:03.125
And I choose to live.

2:11:17.875 --> 2:11:18.875
I'm done.

2:11:22.708 --> 2:11:23.833
Thank you, Viljar.

